        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the relationship between this letter and the <ref target="./DCP-LETT-13076.xml">letter from Francis Galton, 7 March 1881</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Galton had counted the number of dead worms he observed after a period of heavy rain (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-13076.xml">letter from Francis Galton, 7 March 1881</ref> and n. 2).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">Galton had evidently given CD paper to put in front of a light source to create a red light (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-13076.xml">letter from Francis Galton, 7 March 1881</ref> and n. 3).</note>
        </div>
    
